# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-operational-runbook
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Provide the day-to-day operational runbook for the cluster. This defines the
#   standard operating procedures (SOPs) for routine tasks.
#
# Daily Tasks:
#   - Run cluster-health.yml
#   - Check distccd status
#   - Check node temperatures
#
# Weekly Tasks:
#   - Run filesystem integrity checks
#   - Run network diagnostics
#
# Monthly Tasks:
#   - Validate kernel config drift
#   - Validate distcc performance
#
# Quarterly Tasks:
#   - Replace aging SD cards
#   - Review capacity planning
#
# Notes:
#   - This runbook defines the authoritative operational workflow.
# =============================================================================
